lender, will offer as much as 128.1 billion pesos ($73 million)
of bonds in the local market tomorrow.  The Bogota-based bank will offer 60 billion pesos of the
securities and make an additional 68.1 billion pesos available
if there is sufficient demand, according to a May 4 statement on
